RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

01-1222. Dardinger v. Anthem Blue Cross & Blue Shield.

Licking App. Nos. 99CA127 and 99CA136. Reported at 93 Ohio St.3d 1451, 756 N.E.2d 115. On motion for reconsideration of court’s denial of cross-appeal. Motion denied.

Moyer, C.J., Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., dissent.
